        "content": "## Setup checklist\n- Env vars: META_VERIFY_TOKEN, META_PAGE_ACCESS_TOKEN, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID\n- Credentials to attach: Postgres (conversations/messages tables), Telegram API\n- See README.md in this folder for DB schema + full setup steps\n- TODO before go-live: fill in the KB text inside \"Code - Build LLM Prompt\", the Uzbek wording inside \"Code - Static Template Lookup\" and \"Set - Handoff Message\", and tune the confidence threshold in \"Switch - Route Intent\" (starts at 0.7)",
